This sample showcases the Filtering capability of GridDataControl. Essential GridDataControl allows you to restrict the display of records using a mechanism called Filters. A filter lets you to extract a subset of records that meet certain filter criteria. Filters can be applied to one or more columns. When this feature is enabled, every column header displays a filter icon. Clicking this icon opens a drop-down list, which has various options for searching, sorting, Advanced Filtering. 
